<i>noun</i>: 비난 [비ː난], 매도 [매ː도] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>비난 [비ː난]</dt><br>
<dd>blame; condemnation; criticism</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람의 잘못이나 결점에 대하여 나쁘게 말함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of speaking unfavorably about others' mistakes or flaws.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>매도 [매ː도]</dt><br>
<dd>condemnation; denouncement</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람을 심하게 비난하며 몰아세움.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of blaming someone harshly.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>